          "process_md": "**Step 1:** To avail of the benefits of the scheme, the applicant needs to contact their respective school or college administration.\n**Step 2:** Submit copies of all the mandatory documents (self-attested, if required) to the school/college.\n**Step 3:** The school will visit the [Shala Darpan, Rajasthan](https://rajshaladarpan.rajasthan.gov.in/SD4/Home/Public2/Default.aspx) Portal.\n**Step 4:** Using the school&amp;#39;s login credentials (Login ID and Password), the school will fill and submit the application form. \n"
