      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The applicant should be a native of Rajasthan.\n   1. The applicant should be a student currently enrolled in Class 10 or Class 12.\n   1. The student should be studying in a government school, a recognized private school, or a Swami Vivekanand Model School located in Rajasthan.\n   1. For Class 10 applicants, a minimum of 50% marks should have been secured in Class 9. For Class 12 applicants, at least 50% marks should have been obtained in Class 11.\n   1. The applicant should have appeared for and qualified in the State Talent Search Examination conducted by the Board of Secondary Education, Rajasthan.\n   1. To be considered for selection, the applicant should have scored a minimum of 80% marks in the Talent Search Examination.\n\n",
